name: SFrameReadingError
desc: An error when reading a Turi Create scalable data frame.

items.name: case badArchive(String)
items.desc: An error that indicates the scalable data frame directory’s archive file is corrupt.

items.name: case badEncoding(String)
items.desc: An error that indicates the scalable data frame contains bad data encoding.

items.name: case missingArchive
items.desc: An error that indicates the scalable data frame directory is missing an archive file.

items.name: case missingColumn(String)
items.desc: An error that indicates the scalable data frame is missing one of the requested columns.

items.name: case unsupportedArchive(String)
items.desc: An error that indicates the scalable data frame contains an archive version or layout the framework doesn’t support.

items.name: case unsupportedLayout(String)
items.desc: An error that indicates the scalable data frame contains an unsupported data layout.

items.name: case unsupportedType(Int)
items.desc: An error that indicates the scalable data frame contains an unknown or unsupported data type.
